OL,5, Pubs across the UK will be forced to   
OL,6, close due to energy costs soaring by as
OL,7, much as 300%, brewery bosses have said.
OL,9,FLeaders of six of the country's largest
OL,10,Fbreweries have called for "immediate   
OL,11,Fgovernment intervention" on sky-high   
OL,12,Fenergy bills this winter.              
OL,14,FThe landlord of one pub in Essex told  
OL,15,Fthe BBC that his energy costs had risen
OL,16,Ffrom about #13,000 a year to #35,000.  
OL,18,FPub owners said the energy crisis would
OL,19,Fcause "real and serious irreversible"  
OL,20,Fdamage to the industry without support.
